                        <p class="center-block bg-info text-info flowBox"><b>Step 2:</b> Create job position posting, review with position supervisors and revise if necessary.</p>
                        <p class="center-block"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-arrow-down"></span></p>
                        <p class="center-block bg-info text-info flowBox"><b>Step 3:</b> Post position details on numerous job board sites in order to maximize exposure. Allow approximately 2 weeks to gather application submissions.</p>
                        <p class="center-block"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-arrow-down"></span></p>
                        <p class="center-block bg-info text-info flowBox"><b>Step 4:</b> Review all applications. Screen out applications from candidates that are not qualified for the position.</p>
                        <p class="center-block"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-arrow-down"></span></p>
                        <p class="center-block bg-info text-info flowBox"><b>Step 5:</b> Contact selected candidates. Done!</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-xs-6 text-center">
                        <p class="center-block"><span class="btn btn-warning btn-lg eaButton">EmployeeArray[ ]</span></p>
                        <p class="center-block"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-arrow-down"></span></p>
                        <p class="center-block bg-info text-info flowBox"><b>Step 2:</b> Search EA[ ]'s database for job candidates that match the position requirements.</p>
                        <p class="center-block"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-arrow-down"></span></p>
                        <p class="center-block bg-info text-info flowBox"><b>Step 3:</b> Contact selected candidates. Done!</p>
                    </div>
                    
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
